Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.17,0:00:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.92,0:00:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.05,0:00:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!終於到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.83,0:00:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史派克…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.83,0:00:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你平安完成任務了，史派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.26,0:00:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這、這個聲音是?\N- 該不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下?為什麼會來這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.77,0:00:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天為了慶祝你達成任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.21,0:00:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家決定舉辦盛大的餅乾宴會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.23,0:00:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起來吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.36,0:00:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?嗚嗚嗚…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.92,0:00:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經歷了不少困苦吧，史派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.73,0:00:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，在下惶恐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.40,0:01:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種考驗確實讓你受了不少苦\N也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.23,0:01:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,("說不定"音似"考驗")
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.05,0:01:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你很漂亮地戰勝這些考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.41,0:01:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來你就可以光明地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.17,0:01:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了!\N終於可以成為正式騎士了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…進入下次的補考階段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.55,0:01:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，很樂意接受下次的補考…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.15,0:01:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜補考!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.69,0:01:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.69,0:01:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是要將餅乾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.32,0:01:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送往極惡山的壞壞龍那去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.42,0:01:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.48,0:01:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N不論是多困難的考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.26,0:01:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我和妮絲兩人合作\N一定能克服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.99,0:01:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說要讓我可愛的女兒\N去那麼危險的地方啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.44,0:01:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.47,0:01:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.57,0:01:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓你白白的成為騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.14,0:01:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以永遠都當見習騎士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.25,0:01:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.55,0:01:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.38,0:01:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成我就是這麼不幸嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.52,0:01:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…哇!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見囉
